      * Both flow paths (General Inquiry: cases 03, 04, 05 / Complaint:
        cases 08, 09) - this party EXTENDS THE PERSON-BRANCH POC TO
        THE COMPLAINT FLOW. Parties 01, 03, 04 establish the Person
