    Source-side semantic reference (read-only, NOT byte-for-byte ported)
    per AAP Section 0.8.1:
      acm-plugins/acm-default-plugins/acm-person-plugin/src/main/java/
        com/armedia/acm/plugins/person/model/PersonAssociation.java
        ArkCase's PersonAssociation JPA entity (mapped to acm_person_
        assoc, single-table-inheritance with cm_class_name discriminator)
        declares fields including person (@ManyToOne to Person,
        nullable=false; we retype to a sys_user reference and mark it
        conditional because in the polymorphic target schema person
        is required only when party_type=Person - which is THIS row's
        case), parentId + parentType + parentTitle (the polymorphic
        parent linkage; we replace with a single typed Reference
        field <case> -> x_[scope]_case since the POC's parent is
        always a case), personType (a String column for the person-
        to-parent role - the source for our <role_label>; ArkCase
        models it as a free-form String column with no constraints;
        we preserve the same flexibility via String(100) but document
        Requester / Respondent / Witness as the canonical example
        values), personDescription (an optional ArkCase free-text
        annotation slot - intentionally OMITTED per AAP Section
        0.5.7), notes + tags (additional ArkCase free-form metadata -
        intentionally OMITTED per AAP Section 0.5.7 since the POC
        does not require open-form annotation slots). ArkCase's
        single-table inheritance discriminator (cm_class_name) is
        collapsed in our target by the explicit party_type Choice
        field, which is the AAP-prescribed simplification of
        ArkCase's separate-table approach (acm_person_assoc +
        acm_person_org_assoc) into a single polymorphic table
        (x_[scope]_case_party). PersonAssociation.java is THIS
        file's listed source and the primary semantic source for
        the Person branch; PersonOrganizationAssociation.java is
        the primary semantic source for the Organization branch.

